        <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
        <releaseNotes>RelaxVersioner is very easy-usage, Git-based, auto-generate version informations in .NET source code. (Assembly attribute based)
* Target language/projects: C#, F#, VB.NET, and C++/CLI
* Auto collect version information from local Git repository tags/branch name.
* After installed, build project. Auto-apply version informations into assembly attributes. Some attributes are looking for directory Windows Explorer property page.</releaseNotes>
